{"tid":2069311,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"葉劉淑儀重申香港從來不存在「三權分立」","createTime":"2020-06-18T09:32:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-18T13:42:07.000Z","uid":240362,"like":18,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"69c94d0fb7f8197205acfc5134035d64143d0cb2","tid":2069311,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T09:32:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200618/N53G3GID5RNH64MCKLJPUNUJ3I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200618%2FN53G3GID5RNH64MCKLJPUNUJ3I%2F&d=j4yDeGq49jMu68ZzGhcJHj2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=dcbc3242\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200618%2FN53G3GID5RNH64MCKLJPUNUJ3I%2F&h=cf370d6f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200618/N53G3GID5RNH64MCKLJPUNUJ3I/</a><br />\n<br />\n民建聯周浩鼎要求張舉能嚴肅跟進有法官匿名向外國傳媒「抹黑」中央政府，又要求張成立「量刑委員會」，就不同罪行訂立不同量刑標準。新民黨葉劉淑儀要求張舉能跟進司法覆核被濫用，又重申香港從來不存在「三權分立」，強調根據人大釋法，香港法院對涉及「國安」案件沒有管轄權。"},{"pid":"724872ecb78c3f6fc4652dc70b45c5122e10f120","tid":2069311,"uid":251732,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T09:35:36.000Z","msg":"變相承認一國一制根本唔存在<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />基本法更加係廢紙一張<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"010decd50d1ef24dcaebea47a362aac91933ce2c","tid":2069311,"uid":41243,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T09:35:38.000Z","msg":"班親支狗都已經完全唔怕制裁，放晒去做<br />\n共產黨有冇畀過啲咩條件安撫佢哋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddb37f1a26c3b9ffeb5d6ceaf3de23c446cdc920","tid":2069311,"uid":183758,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"010decd50d1ef24dcaebea47a362aac91933ce2c","tid":2069311,"uid":41243,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T09:35:38.000Z","msg":"班親支狗都已經完全唔怕制裁，放晒去做<br />\n共產黨有冇畀過啲咩條件安撫佢哋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" clas